  "link": "https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/areas-of-expertise\/contract-drafting-negotiating-attorney-law-firm-services\/",
  "title": { "rendered": "Contract Drafting &#038; Negotiating Attorneys" },
  "content": {
    "rendered": "<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row triangle_shape=&#8221;no&#8221;][vc_column][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<div id=\"pl-3642\" class=\"panel-layout\">\n<div id=\"pg-3642-0\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\">\n<div id=\"pgc-3642-0-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"1\">\n<h2 id=\"panel-3642-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-headline panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\">Contract Drafting Attorneys in  Fresno &amp; Fresnno County<\/h2>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"pg-3642-1\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\">\n<div id=\"pgc-3642-1-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"0.5\">\n<div id=\"panel-3642-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\">\n<div class=\"textwidget\">\n<p>A well-written contract can help protect you and your business from professional, financial, and legal issues down the road. A poorly written one, however, will subject you and your business to significant risks. Every person signs a contract at some point in their life, whether that is buying a car, renting an apartment, buying a home, borrowing money, or being hired for a job.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"pgc-3642-1-1\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"0.5\">\n<p id=\"panel-3642-1-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_media_image panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\">For this reason, it\u2019s often in your best interest to work with a contract drafting attorney who can ensure that any documentation offers comprehensive protection for all parties.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"pg-3642-2\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\">\n<div id=\"pgc-3642-2-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"1\">\n<div id=\"panel-3642-2-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"3\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\">\n<div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n<p>While contracts are a natural part of most business relationships, not every attorney is skilled in the fundamentals of contract law. At the <a href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/about-us\/\">Chuckstern Murphy Law Firm<\/a>, clients work with highly-experienced contract drafting attorneys who have years of expertise in contract drafting and negotiations.<\/p>\n<p>If you\u2019re looking for <span style=\"font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit;\">a contract drafting and negotiating attorney, schedule an appointment with us today. We offer two convenient locations in the <\/span><a style=\"font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/contact-us\/fresno-office\/\"> Fresno<\/a><span style=\"font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit;\"> and <\/span><a style=\"font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/contact-us\/westlake-village-office\/\">Ventur<\/a><a style=\"font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/contact-us\/westlake-village-office\/\">a\u00a0<\/a><a style=\"font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/contact-us\/westlake-village-office\/\">c<\/a><a style=\"font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/contact-us\/westlake-village-office\/\">ounty\u00a0<\/a><span style=\"font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit;\">areas that are easily accessible for clients in  Fresno, Fresno, Thousand Oaks, Camarillo, Burbank, and Newbury Park.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space][vc_single_image image=&#8221;3188&#8243; img_size=&#8221;large&#8221;][vc_empty_space][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<div id=\"pl-3642\" class=\"panel-layout\">\n<div id=\"pg-3642-0\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\">\n<div id=\"pgc-3642-0-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"1\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"pg-3642-2\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\">\n<div id=\"pgc-3642-2-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"1\">\n<div id=\"panel-3642-2-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"3\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\">\n<div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n<h2>Contracting Services<\/h2>\n<p>Many business relationships can benefit from a contract, and therefore we encourage clients to contact us whenever they feel a contract is necessary. We specialize in the following areas:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Business Formation Agreements<\/li>\n<li>Partnership Agreements<\/li>\n<li>Operating Agreements<\/li>\n<li>Corporate Dissolution Agreements<\/li>\n<li>Franchise Agreements<\/li>\n<li>Residential and Commercial Leasing Agreements<\/li>\n<li>Shareholder Agreements<\/li>\n<li>Partnership Agreements<\/li>\n<li>Asset Purchase Agreements<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>The Benefits of Working with a Contract Attorney<\/h2>\n<p>Whether you&#8217;re a growing start-up or a long-standing corporate business, the advice of an attorney can help save you time and money and avoid unnecessary disputes or legal engagement.<\/p>\n<p>While many business owners are tempted to use online templates or boilerplate contracts, doing so arrives with a fair share of risks. Though these may have low upfront costs, the long-term costs can be significant.<\/p>\n<p>By nature, contracts are meant to address concerns and liabilities as they relate to a specific relationship. By using online, do-it-yourself services, you may find that your contract is too vague;is subject to numerous loopholes, or fails to recognize the rights of all parties.\u00a0 Maybe you did not anticipate an event happening in the future whereas our attorneys are able to share their wealth of knowledge to help avoid disputes before they ever happen.<\/p>\n<p>Unfortunately, even the smallest error can make your contract unenforceable. A licensed contract attorney can help you account for situational concerns that may otherwise go unaddressed in a contract, including industry requirements or jurisdictional compliance.<\/p>\n<h2>What We Bring to the Table<\/h2>\n<p>By working with Chuckstern Murphy Law Firm, you will gain access to attorneys who have over 40 years of combined experience. Our lawyers are well-versed in business law and can assist you in creating contracts that are tailored to your specific needs.<\/p>\n<p>Michael Murphy, Sr. studied business administration while completing his undergraduate at Loyola Marymount University,  Fresno. In addition to years of contract experience, he also spent time working for a stock brokerage agency, providing him with first-hand experience in <a href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/areas-of-expertise\/los-angeles-business-law-attorney-corporate-law-firm\/\">business and finance law<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>In addition, Michael Murphy, Jr. studied entrepreneurship and management while completing his degree. This educated him with a profound understanding and appreciation of the challenges that businesses encounter at each stage of growth and development.<\/p>\n<p>As a unit, Chuckstern Murphy Law Firm offers clients a solution to the complexities of business law as it pertains to contracts and negotiations. We have helped thousands of clients launch their dream start-ups and have worked with businesses of various types and sizes, including sole proprietorships, LLCs, corporations, partnerships, and non-profit organizations.<\/p>\n<p>A contract is a binding agreement that should be entered into with the greatest of care, and we want to make sure your business is always protected from the short- and long-term fallout that can occur when contracts are poorly written. Don\u2019t settle for a standard, fill-in-the-blank contract solution.\u00a0 Talk to a trusted advisor.<\/p>\n<p>Find out how we can help you and your business by calling our  Fresno office at 415-217-9456 or our Fresno office at 415-217-9456. Or, sign up for a <a href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/contact-us\/fresno-office\/\">free consultation online<\/a> or contact us online at our <a href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/contact-us\/fresno-office\/\"> Fresno<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/contact-us\/westlake-village-office\/\">Fresno<\/a> offices.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row triangle_shape=&#8221;no&#8221;][vc_column][vc_empty_space][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n<\/div>",
    "protected": false
  },
